979_802x818.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd70b50f2-d812-4568-bac1-737ff0568979_802x818.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这是一项了不起的宏观经济壮举。很少有人认为美联储能够在不导致大量人失业的情况下平息大流行后的通货膨胀，但<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-did-the-us-achieve-a-soft-landing">不知何故，他们成功了</a>。</p><p>下一个大问题是：美联储今年会降息吗？这一决定可能会带来巨额财富，美国经济的短期命运也可能如此。但答案却令人惊讶地不清楚。杰罗姆·鲍威尔最近淡化了三月份降息的可能性：</p><blockquote><p>杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）向渴望央行开始降息的交易员发出了明确的信息：不要那么快……鲍威尔强烈回绝了在三月份的下一次会议上采取第一步行动的希望，称在等待过程中不太可能那么快采取行动了解更多迹象表明通胀正在持续回落至目标。</p></blockquote><p>不尽快降息的明显原因是经济表现良好。标准的宏观经济直觉表明，当每个人都有工作并且工资上涨时，人们就会购买更多的东西，这最终会给价格带来上行压力。因此，货币政策的一项基本策略是依靠强劲的经济。</p><p>最重要的是，人们普遍的直觉是“如果它没有坏，就不要修理它”。如果到目前为止 5.33% 的利率还没有损害实体经济，并且已经成功地将通胀率降至目标水平，那么你为什么要通过回到低利率来破坏现状呢？</p><p>话虽这么说，我确实认为美联储很可能很快就会开始降息，即使不是在三月份，也会在三个月后的某个时候。基本上有三个理由说明它是有意义的。首先，最乐观的是，我们的生产率似乎正在加速增长。</p><h4>生产率增长看起来正在加速</h4><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/three-reasons-the-federal-reserve">阅读更多</a></p>; 
Biden should run on a message of abundanceThings are going pretty well in America, and Biden's policies have largely helped. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/biden-should-run-on-a-message-of https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/biden-should-run-on-a-message-ofNoah Smith Thu, 01 Feb 2024 10:38:56 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg" width="716" height="487.98809523809524" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:916,&quot;width&quot;:1344,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:716,&quot;bytes&quot;:105751,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7f44cf91-2932-4eb2-8251-ccbd83d779dd_1344x916.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">照片由<a href="https://unsplash.com/@aaronburden?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Aaron Burden</a>在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/flag-of-usa-on-grass-field-9C8r4QUwZRQ?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上拍摄</figcaption></figure></div><p>总统竞选活动正在升温，很快乔·拜登就必须为自己的连任辩护。当然，他总是可以依靠负面信息——<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/a-vote-for-trump-is-a-vote-for-chaos">唐纳德·特朗普是混乱的推动者</a>，而且<a href="https://twitter.com/ArmandDoma/status/1752857671970242636">每天</a>似乎都会有<a href="https://twitter.com/niubi/status/1752727513363579360">新的提醒人们注意</a><a href="https://twitter.com/GregTSargent/status/1752672012584022493">这一事实</a>。但美国人不喜欢投票两害相权取其轻——他们想听听为什么拜登积极行善。</p><p>这可能很棘手；我见过候选人选择错误信息的案例。最值得注意的是，我记得 2000 年阿尔·戈尔 (Al Gore) 试图转向一种“ <a href="https://slate.com/news-and-politics/2002/08/al-gore-s-bogus-defense-of-his-populist-message.html">人民与强权</a>”的左翼民粹主义信息。对于一位刚刚担任副总统并享受了八年繁荣的候选人来说，这是一个非常奇怪的选择。首先，既然普通美国人的经济状况比以往任何时候都好，他们为什么会有心情将破坏性的阶级冲突引入其中呢？就像乔治·H·W·布什在 1988 年使用的那样，“坚持到底”类型的信息似乎更明智。其次，如果 2000 年是发起民粹主义十字军东征的时候，为什么阿尔·戈尔在之前的八年里没有这样做呢？无论如何，这对戈尔来说似乎不太顺利。</p><p>我认为拜登可能会犯类似的错误。他对以色列的支持激怒了一些左倾年轻人（在<a href="https://twitter.com/micsolana/status/1752718669782642810">TikTok 的帮助</a>下）。弥补这一弱点的一种方法可能是接受左倾年轻人喜欢的一些东西，例如在气候政策上的左派立场。在我看来，这是一个错误。</p><h4>拜登为我们提供了更便宜的能源，并在此过程中打击了气候变化</h4><p>大多数左翼气候活动人士，包括日出运动、灭绝叛乱、格蕾塔·桑伯格等，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/our-climate-change-debates-are-out">在精神上仍然停留在2010年或更早的世界</a>。在这种世界观中，只有富裕国家人民立即采取惩罚性的消费减少才能避免灾难性的全球灾难。很久以前这可能是真的，但今天这纯粹是幻想。首先，相对于中国和亚洲其他国家，发达国家作为全球碳排放源的地位正在<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/annual-co2-emissions-per-country?time=1850..latest&amp;country=CHN~USA~OWID_EUR~Asia+%28excl.+China+and+India%29">迅速缩小</a>（不，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/no-the-us-didnt-outsource-our-carbon">这不是因为外包</a>）。</p><p>但更重要的是，技术的巨大变革意味着世界不再面临维持现代生活水平和拯救气候免遭灾难之间的选择。廉价的太阳能和电池——它们的价格还在逐年下降——<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/our-climate-change-debates-are-out">彻底改变了这一局面</a>。我们不再面临丰富和气候稳定之间的选择——由于廉价的绿色能源，这些目标现在是一样的。</p><p>气候专家和能源专家都意识到这一事实。企业也是如此；这就是为什么德克萨斯州这个深红色的州现在在太阳能方面已经超过了加利福尼亚州。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg" width="1456" height="817" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:817,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:64035,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3f1a35fa-c8fe-4ef7-8143-71362c131e16_1626x912.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/NatBullard/status/1716794734105203000">纳特·布拉德</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>德克萨斯州也在<a href="https://www.houstonchronicle.com/business/energy/article/ercot-grid-battery-solar-enel-texas-18350609.php">大力发展电池存储</a>。</p><p>如果太阳能是一种经济效率低下且昂贵的能源形式，那么这种情况根本<em>就不会发生</em>。如果德克萨斯人大规模建设太阳能意味着经济牺牲或生活水平下降，那么他们就不可能这样做。因此，太阳能不会让我们变得更穷。太阳能和电池意味着能源丰富——它们意味着美国人<em>可以消耗更多，而不是更少</em>。他们的家庭获得廉价的电力，他们从太阳能海水淡化中获得廉价的水，等等。</p><p>我认为<em>这</em>是拜登需要的气候信息。他的标志性气候政策被称为“减少通货膨胀法案”是有原因的。这个想法是，来自太阳能和风能的更便宜的电力将降低公司的成本，从而降低通货膨胀。爱尔兰共和军可能还没有采取任何措施来降低通货膨胀，但他们给它起这个名字的事实表明，民主党人明确地将其视为一项<em>能源丰富政策</em>。因此，一个好消息是，我们正在为美国人提供更便宜、更充足的电力，同时在此过程中应对气候变化。</p><p><a href="https://www.slowboring.com/p/climate-is-the-problem">马特·伊格莱西亚斯在最近的一篇文章中认为</a>，拜登应该完全关注廉价能源的总体信息，而不是具体的气候变化信息：</p><blockquote><p>拜登制定了<em>迄今为止</em>美国历史上最重要的气候政策……[但是]拜登和民主党应该在能源问题上进行无情的三角测量，吹嘘他们成功的所有上述[能源]政策，基本上永远不要提及气候改变，而不是制定任何新的以气候为重点的政策。</p></blockquote><p>我认为这个建议有其可取之处。例如，拜登绝对应该吹嘘他帮助将美国石油产量推至历史新高的事实： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg" width="970" height="647" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a1b17b85-1c01-4e81-b7b6-d4bb2553ecf7_970x647.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:6