政府继续发放石油和天然气许可证，并且发放<a href="https://news.yahoo.com/biden-granted-more-oil-and-gas-drilling-permits-than-trump-in-his-first-2-years-in-office-190528616.html">速度略快</a>于他的前任唐纳德·特朗普。拜登去年签署的医疗保健和能源法案，即名字尴尬的<a href="https://www.naturalgasintel.com/why-is-inflation-reduction-act-a-big-deal-for-natural-gas-oil-industries/">《抑制通货膨胀法案</a>》，将联邦土地上的风能和太阳能项目的石油和天然气租赁拍卖捆绑在一起，并支持墨西哥湾和阿拉斯加库克湾的此类租赁。</p></blockquote><p>这导致天然气价格走低。现在汽油比十年前便宜，而且相对于平均工资便宜<em>得多</em>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F182abf01-e110-46cb-a9c0-a213497eb9cd_1318x450.png" width="1318" height=