CO">OPEC减产</a>！这是拜登绝对可以吹嘘的。</p><p>他还应该吹嘘他如何<a href="https://news.yahoo.com/biden-offer-1-5-billion-222449405.html">向已关闭的核电站提供贷款</a>，以便它们能够重新启动运营：</p><blockquote><p>拜登政府准备提供 15 亿美元贷款，用于首次重启已关闭的美国核反应堆，这是联邦政府加强对原子工业支持的最新迹象……这笔融资之际，拜登政府优先考虑维持国家核反应堆舰队。核电厂，以帮助实现其雄心勃勃的气候目标，包括到 2035 年实现电网脱碳的计划。</p></blockquote><p>这里的共同主题是<em>美国人民的能源充足</em>。</p><p>包括廉价的石油和核能以及廉价的太阳能和电池将会让左翼气候活动人士认为这是一种背叛。但无论如何，这些活动人士永远不会支持拜登。毕竟，他们在 2020 年并没有这么做。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e6421c-8dc9-407e-97fa-51395d8e4f2e_921x534.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e6421c-8dc9-407e-97fa-51395d8e4f2e_921x534.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e6421c-8dc9-407e-97fa-51395d8e4f2e_921x534.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e6421c-8dc9-407e-97fa-51395d8e4f2e_921x534.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e6421c-8dc9-407e-97fa-51395d8e4f2e_921x534.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59e6421c-8dc9-407e-97fa-51395d8e4f2e_921x534.jpeg" width="712" height="412.82084690553745" data-att