m/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0b1f6ff6-4580-4d2e-b4fa-7d35945d9b5a_910x250.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> “ Stancil”是指威尔·斯坦斯尔（Will Stancil），他<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/vibes-vs-data">是</a>一个著名的Twitter用户</figcaption></figure></div><p>一般的意识到，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-804">美国经济正在对所有汽缸开火，</a>自然会使共和党派遣其他攻击拜登的东西。移民是自然而然的事情，尤其是因为外国人正在淹没我们的国家，取代我们的人口，带来恐怖主义，毒品和犯罪等的想法几乎是特朗普自2015年以来最稳定的竞选主题。</p><p>但是，对这里的共和党人来说，与经济不同，移民实际上<em>是</em>一个大问题。自2021年以来，非法越过西南边境的人们绝对泛滥。它淹没了我们在1990年代和2000年代初看到的任何东西： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg" width="1389" height="642" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:642,&quot;width&quot;:1389,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:56087,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c59c0f-38eb-4e85-ae36-a6b63372f88c_1389x642.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：边境巡逻队</figcaption></figure></div><p>这是一个巨大的问题。就如何容纳和养活数百万美元涌入该国而言，这是一个短期的<em>后勤</em>问题，这项任务正在<a href="https://www.axios.com/2023/09/05/biden-migrant-crisis-political-disaster">累累许多民主城市的资源</a>。这是一个长期的<em>财政</em>问题，因为这些人将需要政府对其医疗保健，住房和教育的大力支持；这最终将来自城市和州政府，因为它们被禁止联邦福利计划。这也给美国人带来了<em>心理</em>问题，因为它违反了他们的主权感。人们普遍认为，这些数百万人正在迫使他们进入，而不是受到美国人民的民主意志的邀请。</p><p>美国人民非常沮丧。在特朗普时代，态度朝着亲迁移方向强烈转移。现在，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/americans-are-angry-about-immigration">民意调查已经朝着限制性的方向反弹</a>到特朗普之前的位置。几乎所有美国人都同意边境的情况很糟糕，大多数人称其为“危机”或“非常严重”： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb983e-976d-4c87-a4d8-79927b4c1f5b_867x488.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb983e-976d-4c87-a4d8-79927b4c1f5b_867x488.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb983e-976d-4c87-a4d8-79927b4c1f5b_867x488.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb983e-976d-4c87-a4d8-79927b4c1f5b_867x488.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F