f2c-31b88ac5297e&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&#8220;The art of any propagandist and agitator consists in his ability to find the best means of influencing any given audience, by presenting a definite truth, in such a way as to make it most convincing, most easy to digest, most graphic, and most strongly impressive.&#8221; &#8212; Lenin&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;How not to be fooled by viral charts&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2023-09-13T01:20:51.010Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9b39106-a033-4d58-9a83-ad16b92bcd89_618x620.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-not-to-be-fooled-by-viral-charts&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:136955075,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:335,&quot;comment_count&quot;:90,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}"></div><p>我仍然需要写第二部分。但是与此同时，这是一个机会，可以从该职位上使用课程。</p><p> 2019年，《经济观点杂志》（Journal of Economic Comppectives）执行编辑的经济学家蒂莫西·泰勒（Timothy Taylor） <a href="https://conversableeconomist.blogspot.com/2019/08/uwe-reinhardt-had-remarkable-skill-that.html?utm_source=dlvr.it&amp;utm_medium=twitter">撰写了一篇有关医疗保健费用以及为什么成长如此之多的博客文章</a>。在其中，他列举了著名的医疗保健博客乌韦·莱因哈特（Uwe Reinhardt）<em><a href="https://press.princeton.edu/titles/30316.html">定价的</a></em>书。莱因哈特（Reinhardt）将行政成本的增长列为一个主要原因成本增长之一。泰勒从莱因哈特（Reinhardt）的书中摘下以下图表： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7180f0b4-40b9-46dd-a8fd-33a9dc9f600a_900x726.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7180f0b4-40b9-46dd-a8fd-33a9dc9f600a_900x726.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7180f0b4-40b9-46dd-a8fd-33a9dc9f600a_900x726.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7180f0b4-40b9-46dd-a8fd-33a9dc9f600a_900x726.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7180f0b4-40b9-46dd-a8fd-33a9dc9f600a_900x726.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7180f0b4-40b9-46dd-a8fd-33a9dc9f600a_900x726.jpeg" width="678" height="546.92" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7180f0b4-40b9-46dd-a8fd-33a9dc9f600a_900x726.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscr