3-9f54-b0de04241d93_520x666.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6f30793-95be-4103-9f54-b0de04241d93_520x666.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://twitter.com/DLeonhardt/status/1744079752904786268">David Leonhardt</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这是一个令人信服的案件。尽管如此，华盛顿大学的经济学家杰克·维多（Jake Vigdor）仍在试图在<s>Twitter</s> X线程中<a href="https://twitter.com/JakeVigdor/status/1744151461456466304?t=bp5oNbZNaT_MbCECH0UKZA&amp;s=19">挑战莱昂哈特的文章</a>。然而，他的反驳试图相当薄弱，最终的弱点最终增强了莱昂哈特案的实力。</p><p> Vigdor确实提出了一个很好的观点，即上面图中的线条夸大了测试分数解释数据的程度。图中的要点是一组学生的平均值，而不是学生的实际分数。如果您绘制学生的实际分数，则回归仍然可以解释差异的很大一部分，但<a href="https://twitter.com/JakeVigdor/status/1744152410023461257">视觉上的惊人幅度要少得多</a>。</p><p>维多尔的<a href="https://twitter.com/JakeVigdor/status/1744152658632417666">主要论点</a>是，考试成绩不能解释这里的很多结果（大学成绩，研究生院，工作发现）。他指出，大学成绩回归的R平方仅为0.193。但这实际上是一个非常高的R平方，因为经济学的横截面回归！如果您有一个解释20％结果的变量，那么您肯定想查看该变量！</p><p>但是维多尔在这里也有监督。<a href="https://twitter.com/JakeVigdor/status/1744152658632417666">他所看的</a>回归仅适用于<em>被大学入学的学生</em>。只看上大学的学生的考试成绩，才会降低考试成绩的解释能力，因为它忽略了所有成绩不足以进入大学的人！</p><p>比喻，想象一下，如果您查看了在NBA中扮演中心的人的身高与性能之间的相关性。并假设您发现相关性存在，但并不那么强，因此您得出结论，5&#39;2”的人几乎可以像6&#39;10的人一样发挥中心。这将是一个糟糕的结论，因为首先，只有5&#39;2”的人<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/VintageNBA/comments/m1rtl2/tallest_and_shortest_nba_players_in_every/">从来没有被选为</a>比赛中心！</p><p>最后，<a href="https://twitter.com/JakeVigdor/status/1744154030975115315">维多尔（Vigdor）表明</a>，一个学生上高中的地方比在标准化测试中得分更强大。但这是一个奇怪的论点，出于两个原因。首先，如果您正在寻找来自弱势背景的才华横溢的孩子（这是标准化测试的<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/14/upshot/how-universal-college-admission-tests-help-low-income-students.html">优势</a>），那么您可能不想基于他们去高档高中的学生来选择学生。其次，根据维多尔的回归表，将高中作为控制并不能使标准化的测试冗余。实际上，与包括其他控件的回归相比，控制高中的测试分数的效果大小只有很少的数量： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg" width="672" height="291.2" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:390,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:672,&quot;bytes&quot;:173251,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F28a76ae6-f15d-424c-9227-37862fec04d7_900x390.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/JakeVigdor/status/1744154030975115315">杰克·维多尔（Jake Vigdor）</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>充其量，维多尔（Vigdor）表明，标准化测试并不是您在决定入院时唯一要看的东西。但是世界上谁认为自己是谁？莱昂哈特（Leonhardt）的文章的重点 -<a href="https://twitter.com/JakeVigdor/status/1744154415764750634">维多尔（Vigdor）实际上承认</a>- 标准化测试是评估大学申请人的重要工具。维多尔·<a href="https://twitter.com/JakeVigdor/status/1744154658686247373">斯特劳曼斯·莱昂哈特（Vigdor Strawmans Leonhardt）</a>声称莱昂哈特（Leonhardt）的线程“可能会导致您相信”我们需要的一切。但这在极端情况下是不公平的，因为这明确不是莱昂哈特所说的： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F75506dd4-148d-4641-94af-30be6d08b9dc_907x346.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F75506dd4-148d-4641-94af-30be6d08b9dc_907x346.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F75506dd4-148d-4641-94af-30be6d08b9dc_907x346.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F75506dd4-148d-4641-94af-30be6d08b9dc_907x346.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F75506dd4-148d-4641-94af-30be6d08b9dc_907x346.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F75506dd4-148d-4641-94af-30be6d08b9dc_907x346.jpeg" width="696" height="265.50826901874314" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/75506dd4-148d-4